GSTRLYear: Intitated 220216, new species previously part of Three species A. nichofii complex (Naylor et al. (2012) recognized three distinct species in the Aetomylaeus nichofii complex: true A. nichofii from Indonesia; A. cf. nichofii 1 from the Arabian Gulf; and A. cf. nichofii 2 from the Arafura Sea. White et al. (2016) described A. cf. nichofii 2 as A. caeruleofasciatus. Jabado et al. (2022) described A. cf. nichofii 1 as Aetomylaeus wafickii.)
